text: Dalston railway station may refer to: * Dalston railway station (Cumbria), in the village of Dalston, Cumbria, England * Dalston railway station (London), a proposed station on the Crossrail 2 line, in Dalston, London, England * Dalston Junction railway station, an inter-modal transport interchange on the East London Line * Dalston Kingsland railway station, a station on the North London Line of the London Overground
title: Dalston railway station
